      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry at overlapping flow-speed envelope. Reynolds number similarity satisfied. Geometry differs from final device in impeller-tip clearance by ~8 µm following v3r2 revision — the same revision that post-dates the experimental dataset. Similarity gap reduces achieved level to 3 against required 4."
