      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on literature precedent for rotating machinery hemolysis. Hemolysis power-law coefficients from Giersiepen et al. Sensitivity study shows ±15% NIH variation across turbulence model choices — a known model-form uncertainty that was not fully resolved at MRL 5. Achieved level 3 below required 4."
    },
