      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ performed over inlet flow rate, rotational speed, and blood viscosity. Input distributions sourced from clinical VAD operating data (post-revision boundary condition dataset, dataVintage 2025-11-18) and literature viscosity data. The experimental hemolysis dataset (dataVintage 2025-10-17) predates the model revision of 2025-11-10; the team asserts the impeller-tip clearance change and turbulence coefficient update introduced in v3r2 do not alter the input parameter space relevant to the frozen dataset, but no sensitivity analysis quantifying the effect of those changes on model inputs has been provided. Achieved level 3 below required 4."
