      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulation input parameters demonstrated equivalent to experimental test conditions through direct mapping or documented similarity rationale.",
      "rationale": "Input parameter equivalency was established between the simulation and the 2025-10-17 experimental dataset for model revision v3r1. Following the v3r2 revision, the impeller-tip clearance geometry was updated; the equivalency mapping was not re-performed against the experimental dataset. The assessment team notes this as a documentation gap rather than a substantive discrepancy, but the formal equivalency demonstration is absent for the current model revision. Achieved level 2 below required level 3."
